## **1.7 Essential Grammatical Elements in ggplot2: geom 1.7.1 Geometric Objects: geom_bar**


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(data=exam_data, 
       aes(x=RACE)) +
  geom_bar()
```

